<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .proposal-title {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .cta-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 8px 0 20px;
            color: #0066cc;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 2px solid #ddd;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .lang-label {
            font-size: 0.75em;
            color: #999;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {% set call_title = object.call.title if object.call else '' %}
    {% set owner_name = object.owner.get_full_name() or object.owner.username if object.owner else '' %}
    <p class="lang-label">Deutsch</p>

    <p>Es ist eine neue (oder überarbeitete) Einreichung für <span class="proposal-title">"{{ call_title }}"</span> eingegangen:</p>

    <p><strong>Titel:</strong> <span class="proposal-title">{{ object.title }}</span><br>
    <strong>Einreicher:</strong> {{ owner_name }}</p>

    <p>Die Einreichung ist unter folgendem Link einsehbar:</p>

    <a class="cta-link" href="{{ proposal_url }}">{{ proposal_url }}</a>

    <hr class="divider">

    <p class="lang-label">English</p>

    <p>A new (or revised) submission for <span class="proposal-title">"{{ call_title }}"</span> has arrived:</p>

    <p><strong>Title:</strong> <span class="proposal-title">{{ object.title }}</span><br>
    <strong>Submitted by:</strong> {{ owner_name }}</p>

    <p>The submission can be viewed at the following link:</p>

    <a class="cta-link" href="{{ proposal_url }}">{{ proposal_url }}</a>
</body>
</html>
